The url the web security emulation feature will pretend your game is hosted at.

The web security emulation feature will pretend that your game is hosted somewhere.
The location of the hosted file matters, because that indicates wether or not certain WWW requests need to be authorized trough a crossdomain.xml file or not.
See TODO:Juan insert link plz,  for a complete overview of the webplayer's security model.
BEGIN EX

	EditorSettings.webSecurityEmulationHostUrl = "http://somedomain.com/games/somegame.unity3d";
END EX